[assistant] Fixed the new failure in:
[assistant] 
[assistant] `tests/src/org.mockito/mockito-core/5.0.0/src/test/java/org_mockito/mockito_core/ByteBuddyCrossClassLoaderSerializationSupportInnerCrossClassLoaderSerializationProxyTest.java`
[assistant] 
[assistant] Cause:
[assistant] - The isolated Mockito classloader still inherited the project test resource:
[assistant]   - `mockito-extensions/org.mockito.plugins.MockResolver`
[assistant] - That resource points to `PluginInitializerTest$CountingMockResolver`, loaded from the parent classloader.
[assistant] - The isolated Mockito copy loads its own `org.mockito.plugins.MockResolver`, so casting the parent-loaded resolver caused:
