[assistant] 
[assistant] Change:
[assistant] - Added `MOCK_RESOLVER_RESOURCE`
[assistant] - Updated the isolated classloader to return `Collections.emptyEnumeration()` for `mockito-extensions/org.mockito.plugins.MockResolver`
[assistant] - Kept the in-memory `mock-maker-subclass` override for this test
[assistant] 
[assistant] This keeps the test isolated from unrelated test plugin resources while still exercising the Byte Buddy cross-classloader serialization path.
[assistant] 
[assistant] I did not run the Gradle command.
